abstract: >-
  A private-sector economic operating system designed to discharge Nigeria's ₦153 Trillion national debt 
  and bridge the systemic 'Trust Deficit.' NUPA-NG restores Community Sovereignty through the perpetual 
  licensing of underutilized state land (via the Land Use Act of 1978), hard-codes an 80/20 anti-leakage 
  revenue waterfall, and creates a market-based firewall against AI youth-job displacement—all at 
  ₦0.00 taxpayer cost.
